skdetail:

Invocation Name: morning journal questions
des:
This skill is intend to help individuals find clarity and purpose in their day to day life.
Ask Alexa for an insightful question to jump start your day and plan for success. A random question will be selected from the database and presented to you to provide better insight when planning for the day ahead. 
When using the skill, you can say "Alexa, next" to move to the next question. At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the skill.
Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
